description: TrStPSCellProfile: Table storing Ericsson-specific attributes of a cell's radio access network profile at a specific time and location.  Columns: dateTime(timestamp), Area_Name(geographic area), CellId(unique cell identifier), Id2(duplicate of CellId), Id3(cell-specific identifier), Id4(profile identifier), vsDataType(data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion(version of data format), TrStPSCellProfile.userLabel(user-defined label), TrStPSCellProfile.reservedBy(reserved by user/system), TrStPSCellProfile.trStPSCellProfileId(profile ID).
queries: Show me all TrStPSCellProfile entries for CellId 12345 between 2023-10-26 10:00:00 and 2023-10-26 11:00:00.
What is the vsDataFormatVersion for all CellId entries in Area_Name "Downtown"?
Find all TrStPSCellProfile entries where TrStPSCellProfile.reservedBy is "System Maintenance".
Retrieve the dateTime, CellId, and TrStPSCellProfile.userLabel for all profiles with vsDataType = 'LTE'.
Which Area_Name has the highest number of unique Id4 values in the TrStPSCellProfile table?
